qiskit_aqua.algorithms.classical.svm.svm_classical module¶

class qiskit_aqua.algorithms.classical.svm.svm_classical.SVM_Classical(training_dataset, test_dataset=None, datapoints=None, gamma=None, multiclass_extension=None)[source]¶

Bases: qiskit_aqua.algorithms.quantum_algorithm.QuantumAlgorithm

The classical svm interface. Internally, it will run the binary classification or multiclass classification based on how many classes the data have.
